Jenna Etheridge, News24Cape Town &ndash; A minibus taxi driver is in a critical condition after being shot in the head in Durban on Saturday, said Netcare 911.Paramedics treated the 20-year-old in Power Drive in Prospecton around 15:00, said spokesperson Nicholas Dollman. &ldquo;Reports from the scene indicate that there was an alleged road rage type altercation between the victim and a group of men in the road,&rdquo; he said.The police were on scene to investigate further.Image: Netcare 91124.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.